# Quick Reference

## Startup Order
```
MySQL (service or Docker)
  └─► Backend Server (5001)
        └─► API Gateway (5000)
              └─► Frontend (3000)
  └─► Team Recommender (5002)
  └─► Project Matcher (5003)
  └─► Recruiter Engine (5004)
```

## All Service URLs

| Service | URL | Purpose |
|---------|-----|---------|
| **Frontend** | http://localhost:3000 | Main web app |
| **API Gateway** | http://localhost:5000 | Routes API requests |
| **Backend Server** | http://localhost:5001 | Core API |
| **Team Recommender** | http://localhost:5002 | AI team matching |
| **Project Matcher** | http://localhost:5003 | AI project matching |
| **Recruiter Engine** | http://localhost:5004 | AI student ranking |

## Environment Files (Manual method only)

### `backend/server/.env`
```env
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=skillnet
DB_PASSWORD=Skillnet@123
DB_NAME=skillnet
DB_PORT=3306
PORT=5001
JWT_SECRET=supersecretjwtkey123
```

### `backend/apiGateway/.env`
```env
PORT=5000
BACKEND_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5001
JWT_SECRET=supersecretjwtkey123
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The `JWT_SECRET` must be **identical** in both `.env` files.
